p: [u'Please fill in your details below and we will get in touch with you shortly', u'The Premium Luxury Residential Project "ATS Tourmaline" by well-known established brand "ATS INFRASTRUCTURE LIMITED" Located in Sector 109, Gurgaon right on the 150 mts Dwarka-Manesar Expressway.  Spread Over 10.4 Acres Comprises of 5 Towers, 410 Homes & 8 Villas. \nThe extraordinary circular construction of the five towers of ATS Tourmaline, allows for an elegant cocooned setting for residents. "ATS Tourmaline" delivers an ultra-comfortable living experience with fabulous indoor spaces and stylish outdoors.\n', u'ATS Group founded in the year 1988, promoted and run by the dynamic professional Getamber Anand. In the short span of a decade ATS has emerged as a trusted brand in the real estate industry, providing quality homes to its customers. ATS today is a conglomerate with operations in across Gurgaon, Noida, Greater Noida, Yamuna Expressway, Indirapuram, Derabassi, Mohali and Dehradun. Ranked among the best developers in India, ATS in the name behind some of the most distinguished residential projects in the country. ', u'ATS began as a company committed to redefining the parameters by which real estate companies are judged. Though an ambitious goal for a company still in its infancy, a decade and a half hence, the Group has successfully proved critics wrong by reining in new levels of professionalism, integrity, customer focus, and an uncompromising approach to quality. ', u' Determined to outdo themselves, they have raised the quality bar with each subsequent project. As a result, their homes attract the best resident profile  likeminded people with refined taste and lifestyle, who go on to become friends rather than mere neighbours.', u'Plan D - Floor Plan', u' 1750 SQFT. p:
[u'
Gurgaon is the destination of choice for the real estate investors in India. Till around two decades ago, Gurgaon was just another economical wasteland. However, liberalization of the economy and the coming up of the outsourcing industry opened the floodgates of growth, giving rise to an affluent middle-class with purchasing power in their hands and dreams for a good life in their hearts.
', u'
Gurgaon became and is today one of the most promising destination to invest in.  There are several factors that go in favor of Gurgaon.
 ', u'
First, Gurgaon is part of the national capital region of Delhi and is well-connected with the capital via the metro, NH8 and Mehrauli Gurgaon Road. The Dwarka Expressway which is currently under construction will further improve connectivity by road.
', u'
Gurgaon is well connected to the rest of the country and the world via the Indira Gandhi International Airport.
', u'
As there was shortage of space in Delhi, it was natural for expansion to happen in the neighboring Gurgaon. Multinationals, business houses, Fortune 500 companies that were looking to expand and wanted space to house their ever-growing workforce set shop in Gurgaon. This gave rise to a high demand for real estate property, including both residential and commercial property. Today, all real estate developers worth their name have their projects in Gurgaon. While there are several ready to move in project in the city, there are also new projects in Gurgaon for those who initially missed the bus.
', u'
When it comes to buying property, location makes all the difference. While there are projects coming up in most parts of the city, some of the more favorable new projects in Gurgaon can be found near the Dwarka Expressway.   ', u'
If you are looking to invest in new projects in Gurgaon, you can consider residential and commercial property options in sector 109 near the Dwarka Expressway.  ', u'
Take the case of Lumbini Terrace Homes, a residential complex being developed by Brisk Infrastructure and Developers. The residential complex consist of high-rise towers with 2 bhk, 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartments.     ', u'
If you are on a budget or a small family, you can book 2 bhk apartments in new residential projects in Gurgaon. If you are more flexible with the budget or looking for more space, 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartments will be more suited to your purpose.
 ', u'
If you buy a residential apartment in any of the new projects in Gurgaon, you will benefit in several ways. To explain them, let us again consider residential apartments available for sale in Lumbini Terrace Homes. ', u'
Whether you are interested in a 2 bhk, 3 bhk and 4 bhk apartment, you will find that all these apartment types are spacious and boast an intelligent use of layout and design. For instance, all apartments have large balconies overlooking beautifully landscaped gardens. And if you buy an apartments in the higher stories, you can also gain a bird’s eye view of the city. The new projects in Gurgaon are a haven of peace and tranquility and put you away from the madding pace of the city. At the same time, they offer great connectivity to the rest of the city so you can easily reach your office within a few minutes. Similarly, the shopping malls which Gurgaon is famous for, world-class restaurants, bars and other entertainment facilities are within convenient driving distance. So these new projects in Gurgaon give you the best of both the worlds – an oasis of peace and tranquility within their gated complex and easy connectivity to the rest of the city.', u'
The new projects in Gurgaon are being designed to give you the best of privacy and access to a range of shared amenities. For instance, new projects in Gurgaon such as Lumbini Terrace Homes has a swimming pool, common areas for children to play, recreational areas for adults, landscaped gardens for socializing and early morning or late evening walks.  Besides, the new projects in Gurgaon also provide 24 hour security, water supply and power backup. This State of the Art premium housing is located at the junction of upcoming150mts Dwarka - Manesar Expressway and 60mt wide sector road. Enigma designed by renowned architect ARCOP is going to be Gurgaon's new landmark residential complex. Spread over 15.6 acres of peace and tranquility, to cater to the demands of the elite league living, the master plan is a perfect blend of aesthetics, technology, human creativity and nature's bounty. The Project has been designed by internationally acclaimed, award winning architects - ARCOP & extensive well defined landscaping by Site Concepts a Singapore based company  These residential towers have been meticulously crafted and tastefully designed keeping its residents comfort & style in mind. The spacious 4 BHK ( 3350 sft, 3400 sft ) & 5 BHK ( 3830 sft, 3880 sft ) apartments and penthouses are bestowed with all modern age facilities and ample natural daylight to balance the best of both. Situated close to the of border of Delhi, the ENIGMA will be redefine luxury &will establish new bench marks for cosmopolitan sophistication, upscale living & international amenities. function tabContainersfn() {
			var tabContainers = $('div.tabs > div');
			tabContainers.hide().filter(':first').show();
			
			$('div.tabs ul.tabNavigation a').click(function () 
            {
                if(this.hash == "")
                {
                    return;
                }                
				tabContainers.hide();
				tabContainers.filter(this.hash).show();
				$('div.tabs ul.tabNavigation a').removeClass('selected');
				$(this).addClass('selected');
				return false;
			}).filter(':first').click();
		}
	
	function searchButtonfn(){
        $('.searchButton').hover(
            function(){ // Change the input image's source when we "roll on"
                $(this).attr({ src : 'http://www.newprojectsingurgaon.in/images/searchNowBtn_hover.jpg'});
            },
            function(){ // Change the input image's source back to the default on "roll off"
                $(this).attr({ src : 'http://www.newprojectsingurgaon.in/images/searchNowBtn_normal.jpg'});             }
        );
    }
    function advlink(id){
    
   //tabContainersfn();
    	var str='';
    	switch(id){
			case 'P':
				str='propertySearch.html';
		 	break; 
    		case 'Pr':
    			str='projectSearch.html';
		 	break; 
    	    case 'A':
    	    	str='agentSearch.html';
		 	break; 
            case 'B':
            	str='requirementSearch.html';
		 	break; 
		 	default:
		 		str='propertySearch.html';
    	}
       	document.getElementById('advlink').href="/bricks/"+str;
    }
    function showhidetab(showtab,tab1,tab2,tab3){
    tabContainersfn();
    searchButtonfn();
       	document.getElementById(showtab).style.display="block";
    	document.getElementById(tab1).style.display="none";
    	document.getElementById(tab2).style.display="none";
    	document.getElementById(tab3).style.display="none";
    }

.project_menu    {
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size:12px;
    color:#545454;
    width:200px;
    height:auto;
    padding:0;
    background:#FFFFFF;
    margin:0 0 0 0;
    border-left:#E1E1E1 1px solid;
    border-right:#E1E1E1 1px solid;
    border-top:#E1E1E1 1px solid;
    border-bottom:#E1E1E1 1px solid;
}

.project_menu ul {
    margin : 0;
    padding:0;
    list-style:none;
    width:200px;
}

.project_menu li {
    display:block;
    background:#FFFFFF;
    margin:0;
    padding:3px;
}

.project_menu a {
    display:block;
    margin :0;
    padding:4px 0 2px 14px;
    text-decoration:none;
    background-image:url(http://newprojectsingurgaon.in/icon/news-arrow.jpg);
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-position:5px 2px;
    font-weight: normal;
    color:#444;


}

.project_menu a:hover {
    color:#4a73b3;
    background:none;
    background-image:url(http://newprojectsingurgaon.in/icon/news-arrow.jpg);
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-position:5px 2px;
    text-decoration:none;
	font-weight:bold;

}

.project_menu current { background:#fff; color:#444; }
